\name{twinfake-package}
\alias{twinfake}
\alias{twinfake-package}
\title{Privacy-first pipeline twin data for code development}
\description{
Generates local fake data that mirror schemas, file layouts, dirty data
patterns, deterministic relationships, and join behaviour of private analysis
inputs, including Excel .xlsx and legacy .xls workbook inputs when optional
Excel packages are installed. Generated data are intended for private code development and
LLM-assisted pipeline construction. They are not anonymised, de-identified,
differentially private, or safe for public release without formal review.
}
